coord-plane-iteration:

This is a hands-on exploration of iterative functions, especially fractal math.

SPDX-License-Identifier: LGPL-3.0-or-later


build with:

	make

run with:

	build/sdl-coord-plane-iteration

or, if no SDL libs, then run with:

	build/cli-coord-plane-iteration

The "--help" will provide a list of launch options.

The SDL version will allow changes to be made during the run.

The "z" and "x" or the mouse-wheel can be used to change the zoom.

The mouse button can be used to re-center the image.

The escape key or "q" will quit;

The spacebar will cycle between manelbort and julia functions.

Pan with "wasd" or the arrow keys.

Use "m" for more threads and "n" for fewer.
